SATURN BOY set the pace while under pressure into the far turn, relinquished the lead in mid-turn then gave way into the lane. VINTAGE VINYL unhurried while off the inside was asked four wide and in the five path through the turn, came into the lane from the six path and tired. TIZ A BEAST chased the pace from the two path into the far turn then faded. SOFT PANTS was five wide into the first turn, raced in the four path down the backstretch, dropped to the inside into the far turn and was empty into the lane.

DOC BENNETT was in the three path through the turn and tired in the lane.
